006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.util.ObjectUtils;
009
010import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
011
012/**
013 * A base class for an assembly instance defined inline.
014 *
015 * @param <PARENT>
016 *          the Java type of the parent model container for this instance
017 * @param <DEFINITION>
018 *          the Java type of the related assembly definition
019 * @param <INSTANCE>
020 *          the expected Java type of an instance of this definition
021 */
022public abstract class AbstractInlineFlagDefinition<
023    PARENT extends IModelDefinition,
024    DEFINITION extends IFlagDefinition,
025    INSTANCE extends IFlagInstance>
026    extends AbstractFlagInstance<PARENT, DEFINITION, INSTANCE>
027    implements IFlagInstance, IFlagDefinition,
028    IFeatureDefinitionInstanceInlined<DEFINITION, INSTANCE> {
029
030  /**
031   * Construct a new inline assembly definition.
032   *
033   * @param parent
034   *          the parent model containing this instance
035   */
036  protected AbstractInlineFlagDefinition(@NonNull PARENT parent) {
037    super(parent);
038  }
039
040  @Override
041  public final DEFINITION getDefinition() {
042    return ObjectUtils.asType(this);
043  }
044
045  @Override
046  @NonNull
047  public final INSTANCE getInlineInstance() {
048    return ObjectUtils.asType(this);
049  }
050}
